r>
<br>
Castersrealm states rope is 25 percent speed increase, leather is 50, silk is 60 and chain being 70 percent (seru horse at 80). While my guild has access to seru (ok we were the only guild on TP to have killed him up until reciently), I never have the dkp when a bridle drops (and they are fairly rare, maybe 4 bridles out of 16 kills). So back to buying one...<br>
<br>
